ygData.messageBody:
Hi to the EQ group, I am known as Surrea Devine (druid) on Nameless
server. Also, have a chanter on there i just started by Etherea.. I
started playing 7 months ago, and i really enjoy it. I am 35, single
mom of 4 boys, go to college, and work top of that. But i am still
drawn or compelled to the life of EQ. LOL! An addiction maybe? I
would like to get to know other peeps in the land of EQ. Maybe a
soulmate on there too.. If you want to know more about me just
message me online messenger. Let's get this game kicking!!! Shari..
